metadata.name: Poolside #1
metadata.description:
Abandoned places hold a thing of beauty.  
They stand for forgotten memories.  
Often you can feel the emotions that have been lived there.  
There's nostalgia in the air.  
And also melancholia, longing to mend what is broken.

Left behind like toys that were outgrown they deserve to be cherished, loved and seen with fresh eyes.
